citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:10:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"13d56b5d093237311cfe066cbe516291d88ea0f1","tid":1630862,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:10:57.000Z","msg":"係咪唔係黑警/五毛 開POST就推唔郁?"},{"pid":"09630c348aaa537ceee2163aaca70acd100ba2d3","tid":1630862,"uid":282587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:11:26.000Z","msg":"靚畫面要用百幾人被捕黎堆砌，邊啲on9契弟諗出黎架？"},{"pid":"7722a72a33b6656560a4bd256cd4234cfa77a071","tid":1630862,"uid":148253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:11:51.000Z","msg":"唔好再開花住喇，做好文宣先喇，過左法案就整穫勁喇，法案過唔到輸撚6成呀!!!"},{"pid":"dd2e56b6faf1ef84d72bab732b545048cc6c1320